<h1 id=3D"suffix-automaton">Suffix Automaton<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D=
"https://cp-algorithms.com/string/suffix-automaton.html#suffix-automaton" t=
itle=3D"Permanent link">=C2=B6</a></h1>
<p>A <strong>suffix automaton</strong> is a powerful data structure that al=
lows solving many string-related problems. </p>
<p>For example, you can search for all occurrences of one string in another=
, or count the amount of different substrings of a given string.
Both tasks can be solved in linear time with the help of a suffix automaton=
.</p>
<p>Intuitively a suffix automaton can be understood as a compressed form of=
 <strong>all substrings</strong> of a given string.
An impressive fact is, that the suffix automaton contains all this informat=
ion in a highly compressed form.
